videos.description: Florida's John Egbunu almost loses possession of the ball but recovers to sink the bucket for the Gators.
videos.headline: Egbunu recovers to lay it in for Florida

videos.description: Off a LSU miss, Florida gets possession, KeVaughn Allen finishes with a layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Allen sinks a nice shot for Florida

videos.description: Florida swings the ball around the arc to Devin Robinson for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Great ball movement sets up a Robinson triple

videos.description: Florida's Devin Robinson attacks the lane then flies through the air to score and draw the foul.
videos.headline: Robinson flies to the rim to score

videos.description: Wayde Sims capitalizes on a Florida turnover scoring and drawing the foul at the rim.
videos.headline: Florida turnover leads to LSU basket

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza tosses a no-look lob for Devin Robinson to catch and dunk in.
videos.headline: No-look pass sets up Robinson to catch and slam

videos.description: No. 25 Florida hits a school-record 19 3-pointers in a 106-71 win against LSU.
videos.headline: Florida sets school record in rout of LSU
